dogs.name: Golden Retriever
dogs.description: Friendly, intelligent, and devoted. Golden Retrievers are known for their friendly and tolerant attitude.

dogs.name: Labrador Retriever
dogs.description: Friendly, outgoing, and high-spirited. Labradors are famously friendly and make great family pets.

dogs.name: German Shepherd
dogs.description: Confident, courageous, and smart. German Shepherds are highly versatile working dogs.

dogs.name: Bulldog
dogs.description: Docile, willful, and friendly. Bulldogs are calm and courageous.

dogs.name: Beagle
dogs.description: Curious, friendly, and merry. Beagles are known for their excellent tracking abilities.

dogs.name: Poodle
dogs.description: Active, proud, and very smart. Poodles are known for their distinctive appearance and intelligence.

dogs.name: Siberian Husky
dogs.description: Loyal, mischievous, and outgoing. Huskies are known for their endurance and friendly demeanor.

dogs.name: Dachshund
dogs.description: Curious, friendly, and spunky. Dachshunds are known for their unique shape and lively personality.

dogs.name: Pomeranian
dogs.description: Inquisitive, bold, and lively. Pomeranians are small in size but big in personality.

dogs.name: Chihuahua
dogs.description: Charming, graceful, and sassy. Chihuahuas are known for their tiny size and large personality.
